{"tid":2357243,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光：支持香港青年北上 工程大學生月薪保底1.8萬元","createTime":"2021-01-07T09:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T10:48:29.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d3036a68b09971f4ffb8297b2de07fe19efa25b3","tid":2357243,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"施政報告早前提出，將資助2000名香港青年北上就業，月薪最低可達1.8萬元。立法會人力事務委員會今日（7日）召開會議，勞工及福利局局長羅致光指，當中約有700個屬創科類別，其他並無指定工種，而政府會劃一提供1萬元津貼，明日（8日）將公布計劃細節。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光在會議上透露，政府會劃一提供1萬元津貼，而每個職位最低月薪達1.8萬元，相信會有足夠吸引力，亦有信心可用盡2000個名額，如反應熱烈，亦不排除增加名額。他說，當中有700個職位為創科類別，其他則沒有指定工種，港青最快今年4月上班，明日會公布計劃細節。"},{"pid":"dadb3859474dda8847248ced7ba381e672c9e5f4","tid":2357243,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"香港工程起薪咁低 不如番大陸做仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c984c38706abee71a48424879924c2e74897473","tid":2357243,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"咪又係係香港讀嘅小支支<br />\n睇下優材先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294de1bfe19f739c09a94567f5dcb6ebf8e5eac0","tid":2357243,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"萬八？係咪搞緊笑？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tevi3KR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTevi3KR.jpg&h=502b45e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fff39ca7e1d856ae09c4e6f51516e40775bbdb7","tid":2357243,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"294de1bfe19f739c09a94567f5dcb6ebf8e5eac0","tid":2357243,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"萬八？係咪搞緊笑？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tevi3KR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTevi3KR.jpg&h=502b45e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:47:43.000Z","m